    <description>Plants branched or un-branched, brances 1–4. Stems 2.5–6.5 × 2–5.5 cm. Spines
        usually radial and central (rarely all radial); radial spines 6–7 per areole, 3–7 × 0.3–0.5
        mm; central spine usually 1 per areole, straight to strongly curved, 5–18 × 1
        mm.</description>
    <phenology>spring</phenology>
